export const clockColors = {
  colorWhenUsedForHoursAndMinutes:  'rgb(243, 146, 0)', //orange
  colorWhenUsedForHours :  'rgb(118, 184, 42)', //green
  colorWhenUsedForMinutes:  'rgb(0, 179, 217)', // blue
  colorWhenNotUsed: 'rgb(255, 255, 255)',
  clockBackGroundColor: 'rgb(255, 255, 255)' // Replaced by dynamically set property in app.component.ts
}
